### Objective
Close remaining verify blockers by adding strict-TDD auditable evidence and runtime automated coverage for previously UNTESTED/PARTIAL frontend MVP scenarios, while preserving approved scope boundaries.

### Scope Guardrails (unchanged)
- ✅ Search stays visual-only (no real filtering/network side effects).
